H0.text: Toothpaste, turtle, oxblood, oilie/oily, ade, and swirly are types of what. Gems

H1.text: Toothpaste, turtle, oxblood, oilie/oily, ade, and swirly are types of what. Candies

H2.text: Toothpaste, turtle, oxblood, oilie/oily, ade, and swirly are types of what. Paints

H3.text: Toothpaste, turtle, oxblood, oilie/oily, ade, and swirly are types of what. Marbles

A4.text: Toothpaste – also known as plainsies in Canada. Wavy streaks usually with red, blue, black, white, orange. Turtle – wavy streaks containing green and yellow

A5.text: Swirly – a common marble made out of glass with one swirly color
